{
  "stem": "18670.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when the orders came that Mainz has to be judenrein, that all the Jews have to be deported-- the expression was, when you get all the Jews out, judenrein, clean of Jews-- that all the Jews will be deported, so I-- I helped these people because I felt [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In those days actually, we were winning the war, in '43, he says, but I felt that nobody would suspect me that I have hidden Jews, because with my daughter in the Air Force, my son with the Gestapo, and they're all involved with the Nazis and I'm a Golden Party member-- I joined before Hitler came to power-- nobody would ever suspect me to hide Jews.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, these were about the only people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later, when the war was over, I also discovered that my father's sister, her husband, and two of her children, the one that was in camp with me, died.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But her daughter and her son were hiding in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were 117 Jews that were hiding in Berlin through the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She survived by hiding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only other people I met is the ones we brought back from Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were-- they let us know that there's Jewish survivors in Theresienstadt that used to live in Mainz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They needed transportation to take them home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went there, brought them back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Regular camp, nothing-- didn't look any worse than any Army camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barracks.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some-- some people waiting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were not too many people left there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people waiting to go home or be taken home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lots of people had to return to the different places that they came from.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Couple of weeks, that's all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
